list.abstract: Bag（英 [bæɡ]），英语单词，作名词时，指包、袋子。作动词时，意为捕杀、捕获。短语搭配有plastic bag（塑料袋），例句有“Don't forget to bring a shopping bag!（别忘了带购物袋）”。 Bag名词时近义词有killing，wallet，及物动词时近义词有occupy。复数是bags。

yingyinNormal.en: The bag. Which bag? Hermes Birkin, green ostrich.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把包拿来。哪个包？铂金女士包，绿色鸵鸟皮的。

yingyinNormal.en: This is the bag. This is a douche bag.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就这个包，这是个“登山包”(DSB)。

yingyinNormal.en: So you want me to carry this bag?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你要我带着这个包？

yingyinNormal.en: All right. I'll get my bag. Good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，我去拿皮包。很好。

yingyinNormal.en: Put your bags on here, please. Look, it's my bag, with Teddy inside. Dinosaur. That's magic.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把你的包放在这里。看，这是我的包，还有泰迪在里面。恐龙。这个真神奇！

yingyinNormal.en: Put your bags on here, please. Look, it's my bag, with Teddy inside. Dinosaur. That's magic.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把你的包放在这里。看，这是我的包，还有泰迪在里面。恐龙。这个真神奇！

yingyinNormal.en: Brooklyn! Yeah. Can you bring that bag down for Daddy? Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 布鲁克林。来了。能帮你爸把包拿下来吗？好的。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《大卫·贝克汉姆：探索未知之境》

yingyinNormal.en: She's gone. What? She's gone. She had a bag and she left. What are you talking about?
yingyinNormal.zh: 她走了，提着一个包走了。你在说什么？

yingyinNormal.en: What's in the bag? I don't want to talk about it. But it's not a spine, I'll tell you that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你包里装的什么？关你屁事，反正我不是被忽悠的。

yingyinNormal.en: What have you got in this bag, Mummy Pig? It's all important stuff for our holiday.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你包里有什么，猪妈妈？这是为假期准备的很重要的东西。

yingyinNormal.en: What have you got in this bag, Mummy Pig? It's all important stuff for our holiday.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你包里有什么，猪妈妈？这是为假期准备的很重要的东西。

yingyinNormal.en: Did he give you money? Oh yeah. After a while he started bringing me coffee and stuff. One time he dropped a bag of Skittles in my case. That was cute.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他给你钱了吗？给了。之后他还给我带咖啡之类的东西，有一次他在我包里放了一包彩虹糖，超有爱。

yingyinNormal.en: You have priceless batteries and an atomic bomb in your bag. If anybody's gonna have tape, it's you!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你包里不但有无价的电池，还有原子弹。你才最有可能有胶带好吗！

yingyinNormal.en: I brought a bag on the off chance. And your man? I didn't want to make a fuss. It's only one night.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为以防万一，我把包也带上了。你的人呢？我不想小题大做，只住一晚而已。

yingyinNormal.en: My diner uniform fell out of my gym bag, and they didn't believe I was a stewardess on Air Yugoslavia.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的餐厅制服从健身包掉出来，她们不相信我是南斯加夫航空公司的空姐。

yingyinNormal.en: On a good day, dinner was a bag full of meat loaf. But, hey, you don't go there for the food, you go there for the view.
yingyinNormal.zh: 运气好时，也就一包肉饼，不过去那里，不为美食只为美景嘛。

yingyinNormal.en: This bag is heavy. Are you sure we need everything in here, Mummy Pig? Yes, it's all very important.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个包好重。你确定我们需要这些所有的东西吗，猪妈妈？是的，这些都很重要。

yingyinNormal.en: This bag is heavy. Are you sure we need everything in here, Mummy Pig? Yes, it's all very important.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个包好重。你确定我们需要这些所有的东西吗，猪妈妈？是的，这些都很重要。

yingyinNormal.en: Towels, beach-bag, sunshade, and the spotty ball. That's everything! I'm sure we've forgotten something.
yingyinNormal.zh: 毛巾，海滩包，遮阳伞，还有沙滩球。全都在这了！我觉得我们好像忘了点东西。

yingyinNormal.en: Sunshade, beach-bag, towels, buckets and spades, and a spotty ball. Good. Now, before you start playing, you need some sun cream on.
yingyinNormal.zh: 遮阳伞，海滩包，毛巾，水桶，铲子，还有一个沙滩球。很好，那么在你们玩之前都得先涂好防晒霜。
